    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have an inborn ability to detect and understand magical phenomena. You can cast the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.gpzpAAAJ1Lza2JVl]{Detect Magic} cantrip as an arcane innate spell at will. A cantrip is heightened to a spell rank equal to half your level rounded up.</p>\n<p>In addition, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to checks to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.eReSHVEPCsdkSL4G]{Identify Magic} and to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.d9gbpiQjChYDYA2L]{Decipher Writing} of a magical nature. These skill actions typically use the Arcana, Nature, Occultism, or Religion skill.</p>",
